title: Dragon Con EFForums 2015 - OGG
description:
Audio from the 2015 Electronic Frontier Forums track at Dragon*Con.

33+ Hours of audio covering everything from the Edward Snowden and the NSA, Ingress, and PGP, through cryptography (specifically CIA's Kryptos) and how to file Freedom of Information Requests and Copyright Trolls, to 'What To Do If Police Want To Search Your Electronic Device', and 10 rules for dealing with police encounters

Also includes the annual favourite, Hacking 101

More details, including a full program list is at http://eff.dragoncon.org/2015-schedule/

-
OGG format (MP3 format available in another torrent)
